---
title: Baked Chipotle Lentil and Chicken Tenders Taquitos  with Avocado Crema and Tomato Salsa
description: These baked lentil taquitos are packed with veggie filling and chicken tenders. Topped off with a limey guacamole and juicy tomatoes, these will quell all cravings!
